程序包 com.shuyu.gsyvideoplayer.render.effect

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    AutoFixEffect
    Attempts to auto-fix the video based on histogram equalization.
    BarrelBlurEffect
    Barrel类型模糊 Created by guoshuyu on 2017/9/16.
    BlackAndWhiteEffect
    黑白滤镜， Converts the video into black and white colors
    BrightnessEffect
    Adjusts the brightness of the video.
    ContrastEffect
    Adjusts the contrast of the video.
    CrossProcessEffect
    Applies a cross process effect on video, in which the red and green channels are enhanced while the blue channel is restricted.
    DocumentaryEffect
    Applies black and white documentary style effect on video..
    DuotoneEffect
    Representation of video using only two color tones.
    FillLightEffect
    Applies back-light filling to the video.
    GammaEffect
    Apply Gamma Effect on Video being played
    GaussianBlurEffect
    高斯模糊 Created by guoshuyu on 2017/9/17.
    GrainEffect
    Applies film grain effect to video.
    GreyScaleEffect
    Converts video to GreyScale.
    HueEffect
    Apply Hue effect on the video being played
    InvertColorsEffect
    Inverts the video colors.
    LamoishEffect
    Applies lomo-camera style effect to video.
    NoEffect
    Displays the normal video without any effect.
    OverlayEffect
    重叠 Created by guoshuyu on 2017/9/17.
    PosterizeEffect
    Applies Posterization effect to video.
    SampleBlurEffect
    简单模糊 Created by guoshuyu on 2017/9/17.
    SaturationEffect
    Adjusts color saturation of video.
    SepiaEffect
    Converts video to Sepia tone.
    SharpnessEffect
    Sharpens the video.
    TemperatureEffect
    Adjusts color temperature of the video.
    TintEffect
    Tints the video with specified color..
    VignetteEffect
    Applies lomo-camera style effect to video.
